{"tid":2255831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"羅致光指政府財務狀況是擴展2元乘車優惠的重要考慮","createTime":"2020-10-24T01:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T01:38:50.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aafb2f48ab3a798f8784c8ba2cc204d88b47480b","tid":2255831,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:17:16.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，政府從來沒有說過，不會把長者2元乘車優惠合資格年齡由65歲降至60歲；他強調，目標仍然是在2021至22財政年度落實，但具體時間表暫時不太清楚。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光出席本台節目《星期六問責》時說，政府今年1月提出擴展2元乘車優惠，當時未有預計疫情會蔓延全球，亦未有預計政府需要動用3000億元協助市民和業界應對疫情，政府現時的財務狀況是一個重要考慮，計劃的經濟效益是次要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否要等到疫情結束後才擴展優惠，羅致光說，暫時答不到；又說有關長者乘車優惠的研究報告，已經大致完成，政府亦聽到社會上的不同意見，現正進行資料分析，強調政府沒有剎停有關工作，稍後會將報告交予行政會議考慮。"},{"pid":"c104fdc17c004b81f8aef5dee85b045fab17378b","tid":2255831,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"乾塘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b3a7b8c33f13ab30ee769de0ecdf165a39933e","tid":2255831,"uid":19196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35ace772ba839445e694fb5620628b7738c0547","tid":2255831,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"睇嚟冇錢了"},{"pid":"42b9c9853a80cfa8789314e0938a01123facb4fa","tid":2255831,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:21:33.000Z","msg":"要等陳同佳自首先"},{"pid":"cf752134db9ba521a9cb5c921ed1d287900684fc","tid":2255831,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06b3a7b8c33f13ab30ee769de0ecdf165a39933e","tid":2255831,"uid":19196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1